{"tid":233664,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[KPOP] Mnet 《PRODUCE 101 Season 2》討論區(77) 見柾國如見用陳","createTime":"2017-05-07T16:28:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-27T07:32:47.000Z","uid":14856,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"84cb02f121c8597849e91135dda8e87fed678956","tid":233664,"uid":14856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T16:28:37.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">節目簡介及精華片段&mdash;#1<br />\nItem Support投票方法&mdash;#2<br />\n連登推投禮物list&mdash;#3<br />\n節目中字&mdash;#4<br />\nFAQ&mdash;#5<br />\n舊post及開post template&mdash;#6<br />\n#8至#50&mdash;連登推宣傳板<br />\n</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Fc7g6CO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FFc7g6CO.jpg&h=f2770b31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/eF9bZXT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FeF9bZXT.jpg&h=b1dac4a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/4X9EG6z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F4X9EG6z.jpg&h=4095fe78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《PRODUCE 101第二季》是Mnet於2017年推出的韓國首個「經紀公司大型企劃男團」新男團選拔／生存實境節目，以101名來自不同經紀公司的男練習生為主角。在節目中，男練習生需要共同生活，接受訓練，以及完成各種不同的任務。國民製作人（觀眾）最終通過投票方式選出11名男練習生，而該11名練習生將會組成限定男團進行活動。第二季國民製作人代表將由BoA擔任。節目暫定於四月七日首播。<br />\n <br />\nPRODUCE 101 第二季First Stage 나야나 (PICK ME):<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NIld_iEc67s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNIld_iEc67s&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=799718f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NIld_iEc67s</a><br />\n<br />\n新手必看花名list：<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/16mmC1Elk0Sam9aZhEM4ZFgZPE9JkIWirA9gEv1jipQs/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F16mmC1Elk0Sam9aZhEM4ZFgZPE9JkIWirA9gEv1jipQs%2Fedit&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=90bc7c44\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/16mmC1Elk0Sam9aZhEM4ZFgZPE9JkIWirA9gEv1jipQs/edit</a><br />\n新手必看暱稱解釋：<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1wxPMS1mPplFDLAC8bD5ylIvRQ1pC-0OsEVOl4G_yDmI/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1wxPMS1mPplFDLAC8bD5ylIvRQ1pC-0OsEVOl4G_yDmI%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=9ef21753\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1wxPMS1mPplFDLAC8bD5ylIvRQ1pC-0OsEVOl4G_yDmI/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n連登推走向：<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1O2pcionwEU8evmQ4ywFxChjzx2zHiXXHqMDc8AdTG90/edit#gid=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1O2pcionwEU8evmQ4ywFxChjzx2zHiXXHqMDc8AdTG90%2Fedit%23gid%3D0&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=eaa2b2f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1O2pcionwEU8evmQ4ywFxChjzx2zHiXXHqMDc8AdTG90/edit#gid=0</a><br />\n文福黨成員名單：<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1JdR0daioYmz0eKfUASpsmEDMSSvD9kd89LvFNjochx4/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1JdR0daioYmz0eKfUASpsmEDMSSvD9kd89LvFNjochx4%2Fedit&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=11c01071\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1JdR0daioYmz0eKfUASpsmEDMSSvD9kd89LvFNjochx4/edit</a><br />\n<br />\n導師(Trainee Team)：<br />\n<a href=\"http://mnettv.interest.me/produce101/sub/training\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmnettv.interest.me%2Fproduce101%2Fsub%2Ftraining&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=ff11e32b\" target=\"_blank\">http://mnettv.interest.me/produce101/sub/training</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/TMEtEtM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FTMEtEtM.png&h=abc095f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n練習生profile：<br />\n<a href=\"http://mnettv.interest.me/produce101/sub/profile\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmnettv.interest.me%2Fproduce101%2Fsub%2Fprofile&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=39f15476\" target=\"_blank\">http://mnettv.interest.me/produce101/sub/profile</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/yAqJjqK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FyAqJjqK.jpg&h=69e45565&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/ZBrzMbE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FZBrzMbE.jpg&h=1799896b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/GG9PJb4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FGG9PJb4.jpg&h=7c1a3895&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/h1YG56W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fh1YG56W.jpg&h=24fc8395&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/2n9nL2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F2n9nL2e.jpg&h=bae106d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/m2E1vn4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fm2E1vn4.jpg&h=e073416e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/hwim0t8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fhwim0t8.jpg&h=56087e66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nNaver 101 Channel：<br />\n<a href=\"http://tv.naver.com/cjenm.produce101s2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftv.naver.com%2Fcjenm.produce101s2&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=b906e14d\" target=\"_blank\">http://tv.naver.com/cjenm.produce101s2</a><br />\n自我介紹中字：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC8TFbG82l5wEV7kbOorrkdQ/videos\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUC8TFbG82l5wEV7kbOorrkdQ%2Fvideos&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=d5000fca\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC8TFbG82l5wEV7kbOorrkdQ/videos</a><br />\n表演精華：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/PlayMnet/videos\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fuser%2FPlayMnet%2Fvideos&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=86f01ccb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/user/PlayMnet/videos</a>"},{"pid":"f903a30bfee5b945e87a0ed7b0fff17c2b69315a","tid":233664,"uid":14856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T16:29:18.000Z","msg":"Item Support<br />\n呢個活動每個練習生一日一票<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">當然你可以開好多個分身去投</span></span><br />\n揀你鍾意嘅練習生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n投夠一定票數嘅話 Mnet就會派禮物比你應援嘅練習生<br />\n投票係累積嘅 所以投到某個數目嘅話 Mnet又會送其他野比練習生<br />\n夠100％就會送餐車<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/viruJRX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FviruJRX.png&h=61899741&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成功例子：文福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/tBZ7WMB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FtBZ7WMB.jpg&h=75860897&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n投票方法：<br />\n1）入呢個網，揀你想投嘅練習生，禁佢地個大頭<br />\n<a href=\"https://101maboy.com/m101.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F101maboy.com%2Fm101.php&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=47232f37\" target=\"_blank\">https://101maboy.com/m101.php</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/4mOcmNw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F4mOcmNw.png&h=0a012edf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2）然後碌落去會見到呢個，禁呢個<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/5Fs5f0L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F5Fs5f0L.png&h=5ab7fb86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3）會彈出呢個畫面，禁多次藍色就得㗎喇<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/chOZvFT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FchOZvFT.png&h=15a034ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n＊如果第一次投會叫你用SNS登入 用Facebook 登入就OK<br />\n<br />\n4）因為每日只可以投一次（記住香港時間23:00就已經係韓國嘅00:00 即係第2日）<br />\n<strong>每日只可以投每個練習生一次</strong><br />\n所以投多過一次就會叫你收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/N7F8FYg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FN7F8FYg.png&h=c41d9013&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3f52a9619fd12b0d69b52c25b0bb8ccad3036675","tid":233664,"uid":14856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T16:29:52.000Z","msg":"連登推投禮物list：<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/lBaCrwW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FlBaCrwW.jpg&h=2d1d2421&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n101 MABOY 後援投票<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Center 文福：</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"http://101maboy.com/m101_detail.php?idx=72\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F101maboy.com%2Fm101_detail.php%3Fidx%3D72&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=ba3202ad\" target=\"_blank\">http://101maboy.com/m101_detail.php?idx=72</a></span><br />\n<br />\n候選隊友（排名不分先後）<br />\n<br />\n眼鏡男 李健錫(RBW - 이건희 LEE KEON HEE)<br />\n<a href=\"http://101maboy.com/m101_detail.php?idx=57\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F101maboy.com%2Fm101_detail.php%3Fidx%3D57&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=b68aae92\" target=\"_blank\">http: